14
00:03:29,856 --> 00:03:31,816
Ya, saya telah melakukannya.

15
00:03:33,568 --> 00:03:36,529
Awak nampak tak selesa
tidur atas sofa malam tadi,

16
00:03:36,612 --> 00:03:38,197
