Jom teruskan.

57
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:53,583
Saya sentiasa ingin melihat matahari terbenam
dari tempat pemerhatian di Bogotá.

58
00:05:53,666 --> 00:05:56,210
Kenapa
banyak sangat benda yang kau nak tengok?

59
00:05:56,294 --> 00:05:57,920
Selesaikan regangan awak dan pulanglah ke rumah.

60
00:05:59,088 --> 00:06:00,298
Jom pergi, Changsik!

61
00:06:06,429 --> 00:06:07,597
Jom pergi!

62
00:06:25,489 --> 00:06:26,824
Awak ada buat sup tauge ke?

63
00:06:28,326 --> 00:06:29,493
Apa yang salah?

64
00:06:29,577 --> 00:06:30,953
-Tentang apa?
-Apa dia?

65
00:06:31,037 --> 00:06:31,871
Tauge.

66
00:06:32,455 --> 00:06:33,956
-Apa?
-Apa?

67
00:06:48,012 --> 00:06:50,556
Na Som-yi!
Awak ambil duit daripada Mechoori lagi ke?

68
00:06:55,686 --> 00:06:57,146
Hei, Jin-yi.

69
00:06:57,230 --> 00:06:58,272
Apa itu?

70
00:07:00,149 --> 00:07:01,150
