-Mechoori!
-Mechoori, keluarlah!

147
00:12:02,910 --> 00:12:05,955
-Mechoori!
-Keluarlah!

148
00:12:06,038 --> 00:12:07,873
-Jom keluar!
-Jom kita berlari bersama!

149
00:12:07,957 --> 00:12:10,584
